 and geography was his subject.  And he later on did an Open Univ
ersity degree, good for him!  And I think he was a wonderful teacher, but he somehow always seemed to end up in really difficult schools and had quite a hard time, and took early retirement.  Married a French wife, so they have a lovely property in the So
