orth of Ireland, in Coleraine.  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1852626\charrsid1852626 The youngest, Owen, became a doctor, trained at Queen\rquote s \endash 
