\rquote , they weren\rquote t going to be \lquote Old Girls\rquote  \endash  \lquote Scholars Association\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1852626\charrsid1852626 ! Which wasn\rquote 
