t know how long it had been going, but it was definitely an organisation.  Also some of the people I met there were from Colonies or ex-Colonies, so I got to know them. And that was a thing that, though it wasn\rquote 
t an organisation I formally was associated with, it very much was a kind of formative thing in the way I went on to look at the world.
