t was a myth which sanctioned the current social order and current social status. Therefore you might want to record it and say it was the myth with the big M.  You might be interested in it if it helped to educate children and upheld the morals of the so
ciety.  But otherwise it was really a bit irrelevant, like music and stuff like that, to the social order and social structure.  So really, you weren\rquote t interested in things like creativity or individuals.
