\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1852626\charrsid1852626 !  I don\rquote t know what that means!  But I\rquote d read that before I went there.  And the other reason is \endash 
 a bit like our stereotype of gypsies \endash  one of the things that the young men often did, as a kind of post-initiation thing, and to earn money for bridewell, so they could get a wife, was to go off down country, not so much to }{\rtlch\fcs1 
